n in the Official Gazette. 2. In the Companies (Central Government’s) General Rules and Forms, 1956, in Rule 12A, for the brackets and words “(Accounts) in the Department of Company Affairs”, the words “in the Ministry of Corporate Affairs” shall be substituted. [F. No. 5/80/2012-CL.V] AMARDEEP SINGH BHATIA, Jt. Secy. Note: The principal notification was published in the Gazette of India, Part II, Section 3, Sub-section (i) vide number G.S.R. 432(E), dated the 18th January, 1956 and subsequently amended vide the following notifications:— Serial Number Notification Number Notification Date 1. S.R.O. 2535 01-11-1956 2. S.R.O. 3135 21-12-1956 3. S.R.O. 237 19-01-1957 4. S.R.O. 2105 29-01-1957 5. S.R.O. 3038 28-09-1957 6. S.R.O. 3867 07-12-1957 7. G.S.R. 48 22-02-1958 8. G.S.R. 723 23-08-1958 9. G.S.R. 750 30-08-1958 10. G.S.R. 1026 01-11-1958 11. G.S.R. 14 03-01-1959 12. G.S.R. 548 09-05-1959 13. G.S.R. 1140 17-10-1959 -- 5 of 8 -- 6 THE GAZETTE OF INDIA : EXTRAORDINARY [PART II—SEC. 3(i)] 14. G.S.R. 1224 07-11-1959 15. G.S.R. 1364 12-12-1959 16. G.S.R. 220 27-02-1960 17. G.S.R. 595 28-05-1960 18. G.S.R. 195 18-02-1961 19. G.S.R. 814 24-06-1961 20. G.S.R. 1105 09-09-1961 21. G.S.R. 1408 25-11-1961 22. G.S.R. 653 12-05-1962 23. G.S.R. 344 02-03-1963 24. G.S.R. 628 13-04-1963 25. G.S.R. 97 16-01-1965 26. G.S.R. 822 12-06-1965 27. G.S.R. 1570 30-10-1965 28. G.S.R. 368 19-03-1966 29. G.S.R. 421 18-03-1966 30. G.S.R. 499 09-04-1966 31. G.S.R. 743 21-05-1966 32. G.S.R. 847 04-06-1966 33. G.S.R. 1266 13-08-1966 34. G.S.R. 130 20-01-1968 35. G.S.R. 667 30-06-1973 36. G.S.R. 327(E) 10-06-1975 37. G.S.R. 414(E) 16-07-1975 38. G.S.R. 2596 01-11-1975 39. G.S.R. 2828 13-12-1975 40. G.S.R. 154 31-01-1976 41. G.S.R. 248(E) 24-03-1976 42. G.S.R. 627 14-05-1977 43. G.S.R. 24(E) 09-01-1979 44. G.S.R. 1256 06-10-1979 45. G.S.R. 555(E) 04-09-1982 46. G.S.R. 479(E) 22-04-1988 47. G.S.R. 694(E) 10-06-1988 48. G.S.R. 782(E) 13-07-1988 49. G.S.R. 908(E) 07-09-1988 50. G.S.R. 1032(E) 26-10-198